commit_message: Add information to readme and add license

Add guacamole and adam dependencies; utilize variant calling from guacamole in scrunch caller;
update to shared tool and update pileup caller
Make read depth pipeline and fix count to not double count reads
add utilities for computing read depth across genomic regions;
move variant callers to pipeline package; add germline caller;
